Project devoted to Bitcoin blockchain analysis.

1. rpc_to_parquet.py
Code used for the extraction of desired variables from the Bitcoin core using the RPC. The data is stored in parquets and a simple way of checkpoint saves is implemented.
This code uses the getblock() function with verbosity set to 2 to obtain even the desired variables regarding the individual transactions.

2. btc_prices.parquet
Code used for the extraction of the Bitcoin prices for individual blocks. A Binance API is used to extract the prices at the desired times. The values are again saved in parquets.

3. analysis.py
Code devoted to the analysis itself.
